posing as a nun,

00:23.565 --> 00:25.650
tricks William Holden into marrying her.

00:25.734 --> 00:28.278
Gene Tierney.
She's got an ass on her, right?

00:30.113 --> 00:31.406
Then there's <i>Tippecanoe.</i>

00:31.489 --> 00:34.701
