William Henry Harrison

00:34.784 --> 00:36.661
as he slaughters the Shawnee.

00:36.745 --> 00:37.579
[laughs]

00:37.662 --> 00:38.580
[exhales]

00:38.705 --> 00:40.081
What's with the long face?

00:40.165 --> 00:41.875
