02:14.884 --> 02:16.970
Now, get out of here.
Let me finish my lunch.

02:17.929 --> 02:19.055
Oh, Ace.

02:21.850 --> 02:23.393
[Archie]<i> Raymond, I don't understand.</i>

02:23.476 --> 02:25.728
All the studio agreed to
was a screen test.

02:25.812 --> 02:27.981
So you expect me to overhaul my script,

02:28.064 --> 02:30.650
a script the studio was fine
with buying as-is.

02:30.733 --> 02:32.610
It wouldn't be a complete rewrite.

02:32.944 --> 02:34.112
Really just the--

02:34.195 --> 02:37.365
the main character's name,
from Peg to Meg.

02:38.116 --> 02:40.076
