02:44.622 --> 02:46.374
for colored folks, limited distribution.

02:46.457 --> 02:47.458
Now y'all know that.

02:48.042 --> 02:51.212
Now, I didn't come to Hollywood
to make those kinds of pictures.

02:52.797 --> 02:55.258
