to play domestics.

02:55.758 --> 02:58.678
I wrote <i>Peg</i> to prove my writing
was not limited by my race.

02:59.304 --> 03:00.597
That I can write for anyone.

03:00.680 --> 03:03.892
That I can write about a white girl from
London who grew up in New York City--

03:03.975 --> 03:07.145
