a new movie format.

03:28.291 --> 03:31.085
Great, and, uh,
you got the hacienda I like?

03:31.169 --> 03:33.463
Yes, sir, and 100 roses in the bedroom,
like you asked.

03:33.546 --> 03:35.423
-You're a genius!
-Thank you.

03:36.549 --> 03:38.259
Have a great weekend, Mr. Amberg.

03:44.724 --> 03:45.725
Who are you?

03:47.602 --> 03:49.979
Uh, I'm-- I'm Raymond Ainsley, sir.

03:50.063 --> 03:51.564
Uh, I'm directing <i>Peg.</i>

03:51.731 --> 03:54.317
Camille Washington,
I'm one of your contract players.

03:55.026 --> 03:56.945
-[Ace] And who's he?
-I wrote it.

03:57.028 --> 03:58.029
