03:58.905 --> 03:59.906
<i>Peg.</i>

04:11.251 --> 04:15.630
I just don't get the impression
this Rock Hudson is very good.

04:16.047 --> 04:17.924
I think we should give
the kid a shot.

04:18.549 --> 04:20.385
If he's terrible, I'll talk to Henry.

04:20.677 --> 04:22.136
A colored writer?

04:22.595 --> 04:26.516
