and we go find a new writer.

05:15.857 --> 05:18.109
This script does not need a rewrite.

05:18.192 --> 05:19.027
Fine,

05:19.235 --> 05:21.404
then we slap somebody else's name on it,

05:21.487 --> 05:24.407
