and nod approvingly

05:24.490 --> 05:26.826
while the actors don't fuck up the lines.

05:26.909 --> 05:30.913
And last time I looked, it doesn't say
the "Dick and Ellen Studios."

05:30.997 --> 05:32.498
It's Ace Pictures!

05:32.582 --> 05:34.792
Now get this the fuck done, okay?

