-We're keeping it under wraps.

11:04.121 --> 11:05.456
-Who are you?
-Red Tettemer.

11:05.539 --> 11:06.707
Head of Publicity.

11:06.791 --> 11:08.209
No one can know about this.

11:08.542 --> 11:10.544
