11:10.670 --> 11:12.838
-[Claire crying]
-So is my family's.

11:16.175 --> 11:17.176
[sighs]

11:19.929 --> 11:22.181
[crying quietly]

11:26.602 --> 11:28.229
There, there, darling.

11:32.441 --> 11:33.859
