12:26.620 --> 12:27.788
[sighs]

12:28.831 --> 12:30.040
Hello, Mrs. Amberg.

12:32.460 --> 12:33.669
Mr. Samuels.

12:34.003 --> 12:35.880
I'm Lon Silver, Ace's attorney.

12:35.963 --> 12:36.922
You're what?

12:37.423 --> 12:38.924
