14:11.517 --> 14:13.143
become incapacitated.

14:13.227 --> 14:14.103
Oh.

14:14.603 --> 14:16.480
-[scoffs] I'm sorry to hear that.
-Well...

14:17.022 --> 14:21.902
before he became ill,
he became aware of your, um...

14:23.863 --> 14:24.780
race,

14:25.614 --> 14:26.699
and...

14:28.117 --> 14:29.618
now we need to replace you.

14:32.329 --> 14:33.998
