14:34.415 --> 14:35.499
It's your...

14:36.750 --> 14:37.585
script.

14:37.668 --> 14:39.044
It's your voice.

14:40.212 --> 14:43.090
You're gonna get all your fees.
You'll be on set.

14:45.551 --> 14:49.430
But another writer's name
will be appearing in the credits.

14:51.348 --> 14:54.226
I'm sorry.
This is simply the way that it has to be.

14:57.479 --> 15:01.567
I appreciate you, Mr. Samuels,
just coming out and telling me all this.

15:02.318 --> 15:06.322
I'm guessing you didn't enjoy
having to do that.

15:07.114 --> 15:08.282
[Dick] Absolutely not.

15:13.370 --> 15:14.204
But...

15:14.747 --> 15:16.624
this is the world that we live in.

15:17.374 --> 15:18.208
Right.

15:22.379 --> 15:25.799
If Ace Amberg wants
to take my name off this picture...

15:28.844 --> 15:30.137
he can do it himself.

15:31.138 --> 15:32.056
Fair enough.

15:32.389 --> 15:34.141
As long as you're prepared
for the inevitable.

15:39.521 --> 15:41.482
Ain't nothing inevitable, Mr. Samuels.

15:55.913 --> 15:59.667
